modals:
    JboTagged jbotag (Just t) p |-> EX e. (TagRel [jbotag,t] /\ e=. p)

    pu ba broda
        |-> EX e. ({pu ba}(e) /\ e=. broda())
        |-> pu(). EX e. ({ba}(e) /\ e=. broda())
        |-> EX e2. ({pu}(e2) /\ e2=. EX e. ({ba}(e) /\ e=. broda())
    pu ba joi bai broda
        |-> EX e. ({pu ba joi bai}(e) /\ e=. broda())
        |-> EX e. (({pu ba} {joi} {bai})(e) /\ e=. broda())
        |-> ???
    maybe irreducible... note interval-connected tenses even have obvious
    meanings...
joiked props:
    broda() {joi} brode() |-> EX e1. EX e2. EX e3. (e1=. broda() /\ e2=. brode() /\
        e3 = e1 {joi} e2)
        (probably this adds nothing to {broda ije brode})
    joi gi broda gi brode .i se ri'a bo brodi |-> EX e1. EX e2. EX e3. (e1=. broda() /\ e2=. brode() /\
        e3 = e1 {joi} e2 /\ EX e4. (e4=. brodi() /\ ri'a(e3,e4)))
